title: Did Stacey Abrams owe more than $50,000 in late taxes?
subtitle: The critical graphs of Georgia's 2018 candidate were not inaccurate, but not Gocha's moment.
author: Arturo Garcia
vclaim: 2018 The candidate for Governor Stacey Abrams of Georgia owes more than $50,000 in arrears to the Internal Revenue Service.
